{{doc/start}}
Renders a single-row sortable wikitable for a specific recipe by its identifier, showing recipe name, inputs, outputs, craft time, and crafting building(s). Backed by [[Module:RecipeTable]]'s <code>recipe</code> function.

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{RecipeTable Recipe|_base_conveyor_i}}
{{RecipeTable Recipe|id=_base_conveyor_i}}
</pre>

== Parameters ==
{| class="wikitable"
! Parameter !! Description !! Type !! Status
|-
| <code>1</code> / <code>id</code> || Recipe template identifier (e.g. <code>_base_conveyor_i</code>). This is the recipe's own identifier, not the output item's identifier. || String || Required
|}

== Notes ==
* Recipe identifiers can be found in [[Module:Data/Recipes]].
* Use [[Template:RecipeTable]] (with an item or element id) when you want to show all recipes that produce or consume a particular thing.
* Crafting buildings are resolved via [[Module:Data/RecipeBuildingNames]] and linked as <code>NAME (Building)</code>.
* If the recipe identifier is not found, the template outputs nothing.
{{doc/end}}
